metadata.name: Red #2: Rayla
metadata.description:
Rayla

Passionate and emotional, born in a poor family Rayla suffered experiences of mistreatment and abuse in her childhood that led her to have an explosive and sometimes aggressive personality, her dream is to be rich and not depend on anyone but herself. Her method?, in cocktail parties she hunts down the richest in the city, seduces them into satisfying her needs: health insurance, college, and properties for rent. 

With her entire career in finances, stocks, nft collections and estates in her pocket, she found herself addicted to wanting more and more and will do whatever it takes to achieve her goals.

Her "weakness"? children in danger, if she sees a child being beaten or in a risky situation, she will not hesitate to intervene to protect them no matter what.

The Name "Rayla" was given by Josuelemental, Holder of Mono Mood Char Red #2 ‚ù§
